title: #2 - Who Would You Like To See Participate In The Next Biweekly AMA?
body:
With three AMAs undertaken in our Biweekly AMA schedule and our most recent AMA with Frans decided through Snapshot, it's time to give you the community another opportunity to select the next guest!

So with that being said, who would you like to see participate in the next AMA?

Maarten - "On Past Lessons & The Future of GET Protocol"
Laurens - "Supporting Clients & The Users Of GET Protocol"
Kasper - "Blockchain Development"

Voting lasts until Thursday 19th August, approximately a week before the biweekly AMA will take place.
